  "detailed_description": "<strong>A true AAA experience at an indie price!</strong> Why pay extra for unfinished games, with broken code, and lack of optimization when you can get this experience right now at a significantly lower cost - meet GameDev Trash. The game of tomorrow that will show you where the gaming industry is really heading and what awaits you in the future!<br><br><strong>The gameplay:</strong> Game Dev Trash is highly unconventional. Each level undergoes a genre shift, ranging from first-person shooter <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/1bc3d9bb57637c6ca285b10b3236a96d.poster.avif?t=1692405337\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/1bc3d9bb57637c6ca285b10b3236a96d.webm?t=1692405337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/1bc3d9bb57637c6ca285b10b3236a96d.mp4?t=1692405337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> to third-person open-world RPG <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/7755840b0fc99d5d7e186aba764fe0f5.poster.avif?t=1692405337\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/7755840b0fc99d5d7e186aba764fe0f5.webm?t=1692405337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/7755840b0fc99d5d7e186aba764fe0f5.mp4?t=1692405337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> and even horror. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/66f9283f441cc8fc1d348b2036bdab98.poster.avif?t=1692405337\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/66f9283f441cc8fc1d348b2036bdab98.webm?t=1692405337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436390/extras/66f9283f441cc8fc1d348b2036bdab98.mp4?t=1692405337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> Additionally, the game features two unique levels. At the end of each level, players will encounter a boss that represents a different game industry persona, from developer to game producer. All of this is wrapped in a slightly insane plot about the modern game developer and its secrets, narrated by an off-screen voice.<br><strong>If you enjoy silly jokes and unique gameplay, then this game is perfect for you!</strong><br><br><strong>!!CAUTION!!</strong><br>At the moment, there are 2 out of 5 planned levels in the game. The horror level is still under development, while the next two levels are only in the plans.<br><br>Favorite aggressive microtransactions and Day One DLCs - are just jokes. There is no aggressive microtransactions and Day One DLCs in game.",
